---
import { Check, ExternalLink, Mail } from "lucide-react";
---

<section id="contact" class="border-t border-brand-800/30 pt-16">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start bg-brand-900/10 border border-[#1e293b]/40 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
    <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-sky-500/5 border border-sky-400/20 rounded-full text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-sky-400">
        <Mail class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> SECURE COMMS GATEWAY
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-100 tracking-tight">Initiate A Protocol Invariant Audit</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans max-w-md">
        Verify TVL boundaries or request architectural assessments securely. Submissions checked routinely via my cryptographic inbox.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-slate-500">EMAIL:</span>
          <a href="mailto:maxidrom11@gmail.com" class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 hover:underline">maksim@asterdexhub.com</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-slate-500">OFFICE:</span>
          <span>Minsk Financial District Core, Belarus, BY</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-slate-500">LINKEDIN:</span>
          <a href="https://by.linkedin.com/in/maksim-sokal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 flex items-center gap-1">
            https://by.linkedin.com/in/maksim-sokal <ExternalLink class="w-3 h-3" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-6 bg-brand-950/40 p-6 border border-brand-800/35 rounded-xl space-y-4">
      <h4 class="font-display font-medium text-slate-200 text-sm tracking-wide">Client Intake Questionnaire</h4>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-sans">
        For prompt review, please send your codebase repository link, audited TVL targets, and primary mechanism design specifications to the official email above.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-brand-800/40 space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-300">
          <Check class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
          <span>Accepting assignments for Q3 / Q4 2026.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-300">
          <Check class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
          <span>Special discount applied for public-good open source protocols.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a
        href="mailto:maksim@asterdexhub.com?subject=DeFi%20Protocol%20Audit%20Inquiry%20-%20Maksim%20Sokal"
        class="block text-center text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest bg-sky-500/10 hover:bg-sky-500/20 border border-sky-400/35 hover:border-sky-400 text-sky-300 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer"
      >
        Launch Intake Gateway
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
